    "• Bottleneck Adapter (Adapter): The model's parameters are frozen and bottleneck adapters in the Pfeiffer configuration [19] are added to all the layers.",
    "As we discuss further, the choice of the adapter configuration was suggested by our ablation experiments that demonstrated the Pfeiffer configuration to outperform the Houlsby version on average (S3 Appendix).",
